<section id="audience" class="container-full section-space">
  <div data-reveal class="reveal-sequence max-w-prose">
    <h2 class="text-section-title text-balance">Built for businesses that have already invested</h2>
    <p class="mt-5 text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.65] text-muted md:text-base md:leading-[1.65]">
      This is not an introductory AI workshop. It is for leadership teams that have committed budget
      and now need evidence, prioritisation and a credible route forward.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
    <div data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1" class="reveal-sequence panel p-7 md:p-8">
      <p class="label">A strong fit</p>
      <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3.5 text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.65] md:text-base">
        <li>You have already bought AI software, licences or implementation support.</li>
        <li>Adoption is inconsistent or concentrated among a few employees.</li>
        <li>Leadership cannot clearly quantify the return.</li>
        <li>Several tools overlap or are disconnected from core workflows.</li>
        <li>A decision is approaching on renewal, expansion or further investment.</li>
        <li>
          The business has roughly 30–250 employees and operates primarily through digital
          workflows.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2" class="reveal-sequence panel-dark p-7 md:p-8">
      <p class="label">Probably not a fit</p>
      <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3.5 text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.65] text-white/90 md:text-base">
        <li>You are only looking for a general introduction to AI.</li>
        <li>No budget has yet been committed.</li>
        <li>You want speculative use cases without operational ownership.</li>
        <li>You primarily need a large custom software development team.</li>
        <li>You need an immediate company-wide transformation programme.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
